00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
What if your DNA could reveal your true age?

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:07,600
Scientists are uncovering the secrets of aging through epigenetic clocks.

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:11,600
These clocks measure DNA methylation patterns, helping estimate biological age.

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:18,000
Research shows they can indicate how well your body is aging, but it’s not your fate.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,800
Instead, it opens doors to understanding and maybe, altering our aging process.

